:"opening","count":1},{"word":"control","count":1},{"word":"continue","count":1},{"word":"granted","count":1},{"word":"received","count":1},{"word":"word","count":1},{"word":"public","count":1},{"word":"security","count":1},{"word":"bureau","count":1},{"word":"ten","count":1},{"word":"minutes","count":1},{"word":"ago","count":1},{"word":"taken","count":1},{"word":"exiles","count":1},{"word":"custody","count":1},{"word":"found","count":1},{"word":"location","count":1},{"word":"paintings","count":1},{"word":"hidden","count":1},{"word":"anything","count":1},{"word":"else","count":1},{"word":"defense","count":1},{"word":"re-evaluate","count":1},{"word":"exchange's","count":1},{"word":"involvement","count":1},{"word":"incident","count":1},{"word":"conduct","count":1},{"word":"comprehensive","count":1},{"word":"investigation","count":1},{"word":"soon","count":1},{"word":"possible","count":1},{"word":"adjourned","count":1}],"lines":[{"text":"Ms. Zhezhi, the hearing is about to start. If you would, please join us.","quest_name":"True Colors","quest_id":311000000},{"text":"With both parties present, this hearing is now in session. Let us begin.","quest_name":"True Colors","quest_id":311000000},{"text":"First, a brief overview of the case before us.","quest_name":"True Colors","quest_id":311000000},{"text":"Ms. Zhezhi alleges that the guilty party, Mingyan, implicated in the Tacet Discord Assault, was coerced into committing art fraud under duress.","quest_name":"True Colors","quest_id":311000000},{"text":"Therefore, her mental state was adversely affected, which led to her committing actions contrary to her will.","quest_name":"True Colors","quest_id":311000000},{"text":"Today, based on new evidence provided by Ms. Zhezhi and the result of this hearing, we will determine whether to revisit Mingyan's charges and consider if the Shanyun Art Exchange is indeed guilty of selling illegal art forgeries.","quest_name":"True Colors","quest_id":311000000},{"text":"Mr. Baici, I remind you that any evidence or arguments presented before and during the hearing are valid.","quest_name":"True Colors","quest_id":311000000},{"text":"If you would like to add further information, you are welcome to do so at any point.","quest_name":"True Colors","quest_id":311000000},{"text":"Now, without further ado, either party may begin their opening statement.","quest_name":"True Colors","quest_id":311000000},{"text":"Please control yourself, Mr. Baici.","quest_name":"True Colors","quest_id":311000000},{"text":"Order! Order!","quest_name":"True Colors","quest_id":311000000},{"text":"You may continue your statement.","quest_name":"True Colors","quest_id":311000000},{"text":"Granted.","quest_name":"True Colors","quest_id":311000000},{"text":"We received word from the Public Security Bureau ten minutes ago that they have taken the Exiles into custody and found the location where the paintings were hidden.","quest_name":"True Colors","quest_id":311000000},{"text":"Mr. Baici, do you have anything else to add to your defense?","quest_name":"True Colors","quest_id":311000000},{"text":"Very well. We will re-evaluate Mingyan's charges, determine the Shanyun Art Exchange's involvement in the incident, and conduct a comprehensive investigation as soon as possible.","quest_name":"True Colors","quest_id":311000000},{"text":"This hearing is adjourned.","quest_name":"True Colors","quest_id":311000000}]}